| Mapping ID | Source Table | Source Field | Target Object | Target Field        | Transformation                                                     | Validation                         | Business Rule                                |
| ---------- | ------------ | ------------ | ------------- | ------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------ | ---------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------- |
| MAP-GL-001 | ACDOCA       | BELNR        | journalEntry  | documentId          | Concatenate CompanyCode + FiscalYear + BELNR, remove leading zeros | Not Null, Unique                   | Unique Journal Entry ID                      |
| MAP-GL-002 | ACDOCA       | BUDAT        | journalEntry  | postingDate         | Convert SAP date (YYYYMMDD) to ISO 8601 (YYYY-MM-DD)               | Valid Date                         | Must belong to fiscal period                 |
| MAP-GL-003 | ACDOCA       | BLDAT        | journalEntry  | documentDate        | Convert SAP date to ISO format                                     | Valid Date                         | Cannot exceed posting date by allowed window |
| MAP-GL-004 | ACDOCA       | RACCT        | journalEntry  | glAccount           | Remove leading zeros and map to target Chart of Accounts           | Must exist in GL Master            | Mandatory field                              |
| MAP-GL-005 | ACDOCA       | HSL          | journalEntry  | amountLC            | Convert to Decimal(2)                                              | Numeric, Range Check               | Amount within allowed financial limits       |
| MAP-GL-006 | ACDOCA       | WSL          | journalEntry  | amountTC            | Convert to Decimal(2)                                              | Numeric                            | Transaction amount required                  |
| MAP-GL-007 | ACDOCA       | RHCUR        | journalEntry  | localCurrency       | Validate ISO 4217 currency code                                    | Must be valid currency             | Currency mandatory                           |
| MAP-GL-008 | ACDOCA       | RWCUR        | journalEntry  | transactionCurrency | Validate ISO 4217 currency code                                    | Must be valid currency             | Transaction currency required                |
| MAP-GL-009 | ACDOCA       | KOSTL        | journalEntry  | costCenter          | Remove leading zeros                                               | Must exist in Cost Center Master   | Optional but validated                       |
| MAP-GL-010 | ACDOCA       | PRCTR        | journalEntry  | profitCenter        | Remove leading zeros                                               | Must exist in Profit Center Master | Optional but validated                       |
| MAP-GL-011 | ACDOCA       | MONAT        | journalEntry  | fiscalPeriod        | Map SAP fiscal period to reporting period                          | Range 1–16                         | Special periods handled separately           |
| MAP-GL-012 | ACDOCA       | GJAHR        | journalEntry  | fiscalYear          | Direct mapping                                                     | Four-digit year                    | Fiscal year mandatory                        |
| MAP-GL-013 | ACDOCA       | BUKRS        | journalEntry  | companyCode         | Direct mapping                                                     | Company code must exist            | Mandatory                                    |
| MAP-GL-014 | ACDOCA       | BLART        | journalEntry  | documentType        | Map SAP document type to FinSight type                             | Must exist in lookup table         | Valid business document                      |
| MAP-GL-015 | ACDOCA       | BKTXT        | journalEntry  | documentHeaderText  | Trim spaces                                                        | Maximum 255 characters             | Optional description                         |
